article.description: Will Butler had 17 points as UAB topped UTEP 69-55 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Butler scores 17 to lift UAB past UTEP 69-55
article.linkText: Butler scores 17 to lift UAB past UTEP 69-55
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- Will Butler had 17 points as UAB topped UTEP 69-55 on Saturday night. Jalen Benjamin had 15 points for UAB (14-9, 5-5 Conference USA). Tyreek Scott-Grayson added 11 points. Tavin Lovan had 11 points. Bryson Williams had 26 points and eight rebounds for the Miners (13-10, 4-6). Souley Boum added 10 points. UAB plays Rice at home on Thursday. UTEP matches up against Charlotte on the road on Thursday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
